of the military affairs to me.

70
00:03:52,080 --> 00:03:53,480
Naturally, I know something.

71
00:03:54,200 --> 00:03:55,520
If you don't say,

72
00:03:55,680 --> 00:03:56,760
I won't ask.

73
00:03:58,320 --> 00:03:59,520
If you trust me,

74
00:04:00,120 --> 00:04:01,680
I will do my best.

75
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:03,480
There will be no mistakes.

76
00:04:10,160 --> 00:04:11,000
Good.

77
00:04:11,740 --> 00:04:12,880
Come with us

78
00:04:13,360 --> 00:04:14,680
to the negotiation.

79
00:04:15,430 --> 00:04:16,400
Yes.

80
00:04:43,300 --> 00:04:44,440
Meet me in the greenhouse tonight.

81
00:04:44,450 --> 00:04:45,320
I will give you the answer.

82
