119
00:06:42,690 --> 00:06:43,880
Whether it's the Governor's Mansion

120
00:06:44,190 --> 00:06:45,280
or the Ouyang Mansion,

121
00:06:45,680 --> 00:06:47,080
they are gone.

122
00:06:47,800 --> 00:06:48,680
We

123
00:06:49,360 --> 00:06:50,960
need to have a future that belongs to us,

124
00:06:51,880 --> 00:06:52,840
